   {
    "code": "    image_features = self.get_model().get_vision_tower()(images)",
    "comment_zh": "CLIP 视觉塔把像素转为 patch 特征。"
   },
   {
    "code": "    image_features = self.get_model().mm_projector(image_features)",
    "comment_zh": "投影器把视觉通道对齐到语言模型隐藏维度。"
   },
   {
    "code": "    return image_features",
    "comment_zh": "输出已经能与文本词向量拼接的视觉 token。"
   },
   {
    "code": "def prepare_multimodal(self, input_ids, images):",
    "comment_zh": "简化展示官方多模态输入准备逻辑。"
   },
   {
    "code": "    vision_tower = self.get_vision_tower()",
    "comment_zh": "取得视觉编码器，判断当前模型是否支持图像。"
   },
   {
    "code": "    if vision_tower is None or images is None:",
    "comment_zh": "没有视觉塔或图像时退化为纯文本路径。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        return input_ids, None",
    "comment_zh": "纯文本输入无需视觉特征。"
   },
   {
    "code": "    if isinstance(images, list) or images.ndim == 5:",
    "comment_zh": "多图或多分块输入需要先合并批次。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        concat_images = torch.cat(images, dim=0)",
    "comment_zh": "把不同图像块拼成一次视觉前向的批次。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        image_features = self.encode_images(concat_images)",
    "comment_zh": "统一经过 CLIP 与多模态投影器。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        split_sizes = [image.shape[0] for image in images]",
    "comment_zh": "记录每张图原本包含多少块。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        image_features = torch.split(image_features, split_sizes, dim=0)",
    "comment_zh": "编码后再按原图拆回。"
   },
   {
    "code": "    else:",
    "comment_zh": "普通单图批次可直接编码。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        image_features = [self.encode_images(images)]",
    "comment_zh": "得到单图视觉 token，并统一包装为列表供后续合并。"
   },
   {
    "code": "    if self.config.mm_patch_merge_type == \"flat\":",
    "comment_zh": "基础版本采用直接展平的 patch 合并方式。"
   },
   {
    "code": "        image_features = [x.flatten(0, 1) for x in image_features]",
    "comment_zh": "把图块维和 patch 维合成连续视觉序列。"
   },
   {
    "code": "    return input_ids, image_features",
    "comment_zh": "返回文本 ID 与视觉 token，随后替换图像占位符并送入 LLM。"
